descriptionHtml:
a distressed look for the blacksmith apron, in original/ vanilla resolution.
working next to a fireplace like that will quickly deteriorate your clothes with holes from the sparks and distressed seams, while efficient cooling & freedom of movement in working with your hammer will make better results and attracts more customers.

it needs the mesh from:
Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE V2 Armor Set -Work In Progress- by Killer Keo
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3654

and for consistency, you also need to use
Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- by Caliente
v0_2
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666
